title: Fantasy Extravaganza: Part I
itunes:title: Fantasy Extravaganza: Part I
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including Doug Marrone moving away from Bortles as a starter for the Jaguars, Cam Newton throwing a few passes in a preseason game, and Josh McCown's playing position with the Jets. Brace yourselves: Fantasy Extravaganza is here again! The heroes are joined by some of fantasy's finest, Marcas Grant and Matt Franciscovich for their added insight on overvalued and undervalued players.
